items.badge_description: Your quest to quench your thirst leaves no stone unturned! That's at least 100 distinct venues!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 385 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 78! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

Looking for more kick than a session beer, but want to be able to stay for a few rounds? You have to keep it in the middle. That's 480 beers with an ABV greater than 5% and less than 10%.  Try 5 more for Level 97!

maybe this is my first time having an oat ipa but wow this really blew my mind. it’s so perfectly balanced between the oaty, smooth richness you can get from a stout and the hoppiness of an ipa. what a treat!
